data.title: Masako Sen
data.meta_description: Masako Sen , formerly Princess Masako of Mikasa , is a former member of the Imperial Family of Japan. She is the fourth child and second daughter of Takahito, Prince Mikasa and Yuriko, Princess Mikasa. She is the wife of the 16th-generation Soshitsu Sen.
